      • setLists

        private void setLists(java.lang.String listLoc)
        Reads file at location listLoc, and for each line in the text file, it adds the content to an ArrayList. The file is a list of fields that may contain lists.
        Parameters:
        listLoc - Path location of the file containing the list of fields that need to be able to handle lists. This location should be set in the properties file under the heading listsLocation.
